1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:42,880
She knew I wanted that prescription,

3
00:00:43,479 --> 00:00:45,560
yet she still dared to poison it openly.

4
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:47,679
Your Highness,

5
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:49,520
the paper, the brushwork, and the ink

6
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:52,119
all match
what Lady Cheng'en used before.

7
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,039
But...

8
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,320
Speak.

9
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,679
Lady Cheng'en said
just one sentence in court.

10
00:00:59,679 --> 00:01:00,399
But

11
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,679
then, she fell silent.

12
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,560
That's her nature.

13
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:10,439
Fine.

14
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:14,040
Magistrate Yu, make your arrangements.

15
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:19,239
Let's see what she says.

16
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,280
Yes.

17
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:29,820
=Episode 10=

18
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,239
She's there.

19
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,280
Sorry for the trouble.

20
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:42,159
Don't worry.

21
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,239
Your parents were sent
out of Jinxiu City.

22
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,480
I've troubled you again, Mr. Liu.

23
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,319
Why would you rashly poison Wu Lian?

24
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:50,040
I asked Magistrate Yu.

25
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:51,239
They compared the prescription.

26
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,719
The handwriting is yours.

27
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,200
He poisoned himself.

28
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,760
He had the writing forged.

29
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,239
I was careless.

30
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:01,079
I didn't think he'd use the
same trick twice.

31
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,040
What else did he do?

32
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,640
Are you hurt?

33
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,879
He injured his own right hand

34
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,159
to frame me.

35
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:13,599
He wants you out of the manor.

36
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,560
Once you lose its protection,

37
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,039
he can strike for real.

38
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,479
Have you found out who helped him?

39
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,719
Dr. Li handled it.

40
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,639
He's definitely involved.

41
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,120
Oh, right.

42
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,080
Here. This might help.

43
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,039
Stay safe.

44
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,360
Be careful.

45
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:51,560
A late visit, Mr. Liu.

46
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,080
Is your old ailment acting up?

47
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,639
I'll prepare
a pain relief prescription for you.

48
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,400
Dr. Li,

49
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,599
I'm not here for medicine.

50
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,639
I want to ask you something.

51
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:02,680
About your daughter, Xiao'e.

52
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,039
She's married.

53
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,479
Serving her husband's family,

54
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,680
virtuous and proper.

55
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,240
What about you?

56
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,159
A few days ago,

57
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,520
a seamstress named Xiaoyi
had an accident.

58
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,759
She was found defiled.

59
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,199
What do you want to say?

60
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,120
She was violated at
Yanyu Embroidery House.

61
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,319
She died of shame.

62
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,840
Same as Lin Rulan three years ago.

63
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,560
Surely you know, Dr. Li.

64
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,199
Xiao'e also studied
at Yanyu Embroidery House.

65
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,560
Do you think she escaped it?

66
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:34,680
My Xiao'e is chaste and well-behaved.

67
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,319
Don't slander my daughter.

68
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,000
Have you seen this before, Dr. Li?

69
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,680
Xiao'e has a handkerchief
just like it.

70
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:51,159
But the embroidery is different.

71
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,840
Wu Lian gives a handkerchief

72
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:56,000
to every girl he violates

73
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,719
as a token.

74
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,800
Then why is the flower different?

75
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,639
Wu Lian marks his victims

76
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:06,759
with the flower of the season
in which it happened.

77
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,159
He framed Lady Cheng'en.

78
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:11,479
I need you to tell the truth in court.

79
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:12,840
Will you?

80
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,800
Fine.

81
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:18,480
I won't let that beast get away.

82
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,920
(County Office)
Move.

83
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,060
(County Office)

84
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,199
Dr. Li,

85
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,879
do you have something to say?

86
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:27,759
Your Honor,

87
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:30,199
I... I saw it with my own eyes.

88
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:32,600
Someone added poison herbs
to the prescription.

89
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,560
That person... that person is...

90
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,439
Lady Cheng'en.

91
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:41,480
Dr. Li, how can you lie so brazenly?

92
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,360
Nonsense!

93
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,279
You're a manor doctor.

94
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:48,040
How could you
enter Lady Cheng'en's study

95
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:50,079
and watch her write?

96
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:50,839
Well...

97
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,079
Your Honor,

98
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,639
I have physical evidence

99
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:56,439
that Dr. Li is lying.

100
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,279
Present it.

101
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:04,439
Your Honor, these are dregs
from Yanyu Embroidery House.

102
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,560
The manor doctor examined them.

103
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,399
No poison was found.

104
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,040
How dare you, Dr. Li!

105
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,959
Falsely accusing Lady Cheng'en in court

106
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,759
adds to your crime!

107
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,279
Your Honor is wise!

108
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:20,279
I framed her on purpose.

109
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,600
I lost money gambling today.

110
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:25,360
I secretly poisoned the medicine

111
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:28,439
to get money by curing it.

112
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,000
Here's a banknote
from Yanyu Embroidery House.

113
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,360
I'm a wretched man!

114
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:38,879
(County Office)

115
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,800
(County Office)
Dr. Li,

116
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,279
if you want to protect
your daughter's reputation,

117
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,959
confess to the crime.

118
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,879
Mr. Wang, you're the constable!

119
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,720
How can you break the law

120
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,480
and frame an innocent person?

121
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,000
If Master Wu hadn't promoted me

122
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,399
to take Liu Xin's place as constable,

123
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:58,000
I wouldn't be where I am today.

124
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,360
Dr. Li,

125
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,879
a person

126
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,439
must repay kindness.

127
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,879
Otherwise, their ending is very bad.

128
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,480
Dr. Li,

129
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,439
don't forget,

130
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
that banknote was tucked

131
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,160
inside your own robe.

132
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:21,279
Guards!

133
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:23,639
Throw Dr. Li in death row!

134
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,560
Yes!

135
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,000
Your Honor, he's dead.

136
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,040
Get him out.

137
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,279
Guards! Drag him out!

138
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,680
Lies and nonsense.

139
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,800
He deserved to die.

140
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,240
All the doing of petty men.

141
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,480
You've been wronged, Ruoheng.

142
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:45,839
And you've been frightened, Master Wu.

143
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,079
This is settled.

144
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,680
Magistrate Yu, close the court.

145
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:57,820
(County Office)

146
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,439
Who cries injustice?

147
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:04,240
Injustice!

148
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,879
My son cries injustice!

149
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,800
Your Honor,

150
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,879
my son Jia Yi was murdered!

151
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:18,240
(Complaint)
Please seek justice for me!

152
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,720
Present it.

153
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:34,639
Your Highness, My Lady,
please wait before leaving.

154
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:37,000
Magistrate Yu, you mean

155
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,839
this involves them?

156
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:45,000
Your Highness, do you know
who is being accused?

157
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,240
Lady Cheng'en.

158
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,279
How dare you!

159
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,240
How would Lady Cheng'en know them?

160
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,399
Now, everyone thinks
Lady Cheng'en is weak.

161
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,120
Anyone dares to drag her in.

162
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,279
Wang Lu.

163
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,079
Yes!

164
00:07:58,839 --> 00:08:01,439
Do they have evidence?

165
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,439
Your Honor,

166
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:04,920
Jia Yi's body was found today

167
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,600
at the mass grave outside the city.

168
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,600
At the scene,

169
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,199
we found this.

170
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:13,560
Present it.

171
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:14,360
Yes.

172
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:29,759
Does this belong to you, My Lady?

173
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:37,039
Your Honor, this is my hairpin.

174
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,879
But let me defend myself.

175
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:42,279
Finding my hairpin doesn't
prove I killed him.

176
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,960
Now that you hold the hairpin,

177
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:48,600
should I suspect you too?

178
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,679
Ruoheng,

179
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,679
answer Magistrate Yu properly.

180
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,679
The hairpin is mine.

181
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:56,200
But I don't know when I lost it.

182
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,080
Then think carefully

183
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,960
about when and where you wore it.

184
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,000
Magistrate Yu, you're married.

185
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:06,000
I'm sure your wife loses hairpins.

186
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,840
A hairpin is nothing.

187
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,360
Not a valuable item.

188
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,879
If it's lost, it's lost.

189
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,120
No one cares.

190
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:19,000
Since you can't prove
I killed this man,

191
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:21,480
then investigate thoroughly,

192
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,600
Magistrate Yu.

193
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,799
Your Honor,

194
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:28,679
someone saw Lady Cheng'en talking
to Jia Yi for a few days ago.

195
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,879
Jia Yi disappeared after that.

196
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,480
Shall I call this witness?

197
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,799
I've only been in Jinxiu City
a few days.

198
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,840
How would I know Jia Yi?

199
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,639
How could I have talked to him?

200
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:44,440
Maybe someone took a glance

201
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,440
and mistook me for someone else.

202
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:49,080
My Lady, if you weren't at the scene,

203
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:52,279
how could someone see you from afar?

204
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,240
In a murder case like this,

205
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,679
would a killer

206
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,519
allow spectators?

207
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,559
Would a witness dare get close

208
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:03,080
without fearing for their own life?

209
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,080
You're the constable.

210
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,440
How can you not understand
this simple logic?

211
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:11,440
Or are you being used
by someone else

212
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,879
to throw mud on me?

213
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,240
No, My Lady.

214
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,080
I wouldn't dare.

215
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,759
As for being mistaken,

216
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,320
Wenyue, you know, in the past few days,

217
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:26,039
someone mistook me for his apprentice,

218
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:29,480
someone else for her friend.

219
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:33,320
But I haven't left the manor.

220
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,679
On this point,

221
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,399
the servants can testify for me.

222
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,720
Your Honor,

223
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,960
this was found on my son.

224
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,519
Please, seek justice for my son!

225
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:44,799
(Kill Jia Yi. From Lady Cheng'en.)
Present it!

226
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:22,900
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

227
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:26,140
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

228
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:30,100
♪The past no longer binds♪

229
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:34,300
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

230
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:38,860
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

231
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:42,580
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

232
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:44,940
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

233
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:49,020
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

234
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:51,620
♪For your faith that never broke♪

235
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:55,940
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

236
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:58,740
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

237
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:02,980
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

238
00:12:04,180 --> 00:12:06,660
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

239
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:09,420
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

240
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:12,020
♪One thought turns into ash♪

241
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:18,340
♪No future left to write♪

242
00:12:19,420 --> 00:12:21,220
♪If I never fall♪

243
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:23,620
♪How could this waiting end♪

244
00:12:23,620 --> 00:12:24,980
♪If I bear no scars♪

245
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:27,300
♪How could I challenge fate♪

246
00:12:27,300 --> 00:12:29,660
♪I knew there was no way back♪

247
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:33,660
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

248
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:35,900
♪For your faith that never broke♪

249
00:12:36,100 --> 00:12:40,060
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

250
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:42,940
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

251
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:47,340
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

252
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:51,020
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

253
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:53,620
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

254
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:55,980
♪One thought turns into ash♪

255
00:12:57,100 --> 00:13:02,340
♪No future left to write♪

256
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:05,620
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

257
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,020
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

258
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,900
♪If we meet again someday♪

259
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:19,140
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
